= Military

The military is a department of government that is not solely militant, but also provides a work base that helps with other aspects of the needs of Luminous. The entirety of the military is willing to step in to defend should that be necessary, but they are also at the centre of government-sponsored engineering, outreach, border patrol, science, and industry, through their various departments.